01:12:33.583 --> 01:12:36.313
when Maggie
meets Bolt's blind nephew.

01:12:37.386 --> 01:12:38.717
Oh, God.

01:12:39.589 --> 01:12:42.752
- Get out.
- Please try to understand.

01:12:42.825 --> 01:12:46.556
