01:13:09.785 --> 01:13:12.879
You promised me you would
get rid of Celeste!

01:13:12.955 --> 01:13:15.446
We were both naked,
and you promised!

01:13:15.524 --> 01:13:18.118
- Naked!
- Hey, we were never naked.

01:13:18.194 --> 01:13:19.991
We could've been!

01:13:20.062 --> 01:13:23.429
